[4.205, "o", "\u001b[2mUsed: scene_init, scene_add, scene_lint\u001b[22m\r\nAll done! Here's a summary of what was built:\r\n\r\n### ✅ Project: `demo`\r\n- **Format:** 16:9\r\n- **Scaffolded:** `demo/` with `index.html`, `hyperframes.json`, `vibe.project.yaml`, `compositions/`, `assets/`\r\n\r\n### ✅ Scene: `hello-vibe-agent`\r\n"]
